<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,345,1600,1626]" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">Distribution</emphasis>
(Fig. 149). Known only for the Clarion Island, in the archipelago of Revillagigedo, 
<collectingRegion box="[1280,1365,1600,1626]" country="Mexico" name="Colima" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">Colima</collectingRegion>
